### Auto Version and Publish Release Workflow

This GitHub Actions workflow automates **version management** and **publication** of the AI Dev Kit project.
It handles automatic patch bumps, manual version input, tagging, committing, and publishing.
> **Important:** This workflow can only be triggered manually.
---

#### How to Trigger

1. Navigate to the **Actions** tab.
2. Select `Auto Version and Publish Release`.
3. Fill in the inputs if needed (see below).
4. Click **Run workflow**.

---

#### Workflow Inputs

| Input Name        | Description                                                                          | Required | Default                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|-------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `manual_version`  | Optional manual version (X.Y.Z). If provided, the patch will **not** auto-increment. | No       | `''`                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| `publishing_file` | File containing the version constant to read.                                        | Yes      | `publishing/src/main/kotlin/SpacePublishingPlugin.kt`                                                                                                                                   |
| `files_to_update` | Space-separated list of files where the version should be updated.                   | Yes      | `README.md` `CONTRIBUTING.md` `publishing/src/main/kotlin/SpacePublishingPlugin.kt` `plugin/gradle-tracy-plugin/src/main/kotlin/ai/dev/kit/trace/gradle/AiDevKitTraceGradlePlugin.kt` |

---

#### Behavior

1. Reads the current version from `publishing_file` (`const val VERSION = "X.Y.Z"`).
2. Auto-increments patch unless `manual_version` is provided.
3. Replaces the version in all listed files.
4. Commits changes, tags the new version, and pushes to the repository.
5. Publishes the library to Space Maven.
